<s> As my initial foray into non-toy XML Schemas, I took a stab at creating an XML Schema for the XML Specification doctype.  </s>
<s> My goal was to write an XML Schema that was configurable in the same general way that Maler/Andaloussi-methodology DTDs are, and that would validate the same set of documents (modulo additional constraints that DTDs can't express).  </s>
<s> I'm sure I've overlooked things, possibly large things, but the schema at now validates the XML 2e Recommendation with XSV 1.166/1.77 of 2000/09/28 15:54:50.  </s>
<s> Comments most welcome.  </s>
